snippet.title: Best VGM 1041 - Glover - Atlantis Realm, Level 3
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 587 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XLJxqz83ujw
Best VGM 1959 - https://youtu.be/PRCBxcvNApQ

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo 64
Glover (1998)
Atlantis Realm, Level 3
Rob Lord, Paul Weir & Mark Bandola
